30:46.310 --> 30:49.210
So when you add things
like leafy greens to it,

30:49.210 --> 30:50.980
you're giving yourself
some extra nutrients,

30:50.980 --> 30:51.813
which are really good.

30:51.813 --> 30:54.480
And the important thing is
to make sure you get enough

30:54.480 --> 30:57.350
of the right kinds of fat
in your morning shakes.

30:57.350 --> 30:59.710
It could even be like a
little bit of almond butter.

30:59.710 --> 31:01.570
You can add real butter if you want to.

31:01.570 --> 31:03.420
Surprisingly, that's good in a shake.

31:04.343 --> 31:05.640
What you want to do

31:05.640 --> 31:09.638
