1:15:05.780 --> 1:15:08.770
And what becomes reality
becomes part of my life.

1:15:08.770 --> 1:15:10.310
So when I sit down every single day

1:15:10.310 --> 1:15:11.430
with "The Five Minute Journal"

1:15:11.430 --> 1:15:13.440
or another journal of any kind,

1:15:13.440 --> 1:15:16.120
