down, it just becomes real,

1:15:16.120 --> 1:15:18.570
those words on a page
become my actual life.

1:15:18.570 --> 1:15:21.010
- You create the day
before the day starts.

1:15:21.010 --> 1:15:22.694
People talk about law of attraction,

1:15:22.694 --> 1:15:24.220
but what I'm talking about

1:15:24.220 --> 1:15:27.660
is a very real consistent daily creation

1:15:27.660 --> 1:15:29.500
where you're doing it every day.

1:15:29.500 --> 1:15:30.910
At night, you open up your journal,

1:15:30.910 --> 1:15:33.473
