you did and didn't do it.

1:15:33.473 --> 1:15:36.238
It helps keep you accountable
to the actual actions

1:15:36.238 --> 1:15:39.670
that you're taking to
move forward in life.

1:15:39.670 --> 1:15:42.930
- It forces you to sit down and identify

1:15:42.930 --> 1:15:44.420
what's the most important task

1:15:44.420 --> 1:15:46.150
or result you want to achieve today.

1:15:46.150 --> 1:15:48.570
It makes you consciously plan your day

1:15:48.570 --> 1:15:50.680
as opposed to again, like most people,

1:15:50.680 --> 1:15:53.630
you wake up and you start
reacting to the demand of others.

