1:21:32.610 --> 1:21:33.610
Right, and I really believe,

1:21:33.610 --> 1:21:37.200
that you want to look at
the worst case scenario

1:21:37.200 --> 1:21:40.680
and you want to acknowledge
it and then accept it

1:21:40.680 --> 1:21:42.437
and then be at peace with it

1:21:42.437 --> 1:21:47.043
so that it doesn't cause,
