Why wait till the future

1:22:00.010 --> 1:22:01.703
to see the positivity, the power,

1:22:01.703 --> 1:22:04.500
in every experience we face, good or bad.

1:22:04.500 --> 1:22:06.798
Every experience we face is an asset

1:22:06.798 --> 1:22:09.060
if we choose to see it that way.

1:22:09.060 --> 1:22:10.040
Just as the accident

1:22:10.040 --> 1:22:11.380
was the best thing that
ever happened to me,

1:22:11.380 --> 1:22:12.819
I really believe,

1:22:12.819 --> 1:22:13.652
because it allowed me to find,

1:22:13.652 --> 1:22:15.680
to share it with other
people and help them,

1:22:15.680 --> 1:22:16.781
the cancer is gonna be

1:22:16.781 --> 1:22:19.800
the new best thing that
